{"title":"Bronquiectasia folicular","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Neumología/Bronquiectasia folicular-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Bronquiectasia folicular","guid":"Ik0EAh9LhknBZGI4qz0hAw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Bronquiolitis\\Nfolicular (BF)","guid":"Sf_HQyxDYA0U1j-TtTYz5w","children":[]},{"id":"2","parent":"0","text":"Perlas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"0","text":"- ¿Qué es la BF?","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"0","text":"- Enfermedad pulmonar intersticial linfoide\\Ninfrecuente, caracterizada por hiperplasia linfoide\\Nreactiva alrededor de los bronquiolos (1)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"0","text":"- ¿Con qué condiciones\\Nse asocia la BF?","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"0","text":"- Enfermedades autoinmunes (artritis reumatoide,\\Nsíndrome de Sjögren), inmunodeficiencias (VIH,\\Nhipogammaglobulinemia), postrasplante (médula\\Nósea, pulmón) (2-4)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"0","text":"- ¿Cuáles son las\\Nmanifestaciones clínicas de la\\NBF?","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"0","text":"- Tos seca, disnea de esfuerzo, sibilancias,\\Ninfecciones respiratorias recurrentes, inicio\\Ninsidioso, curso crónico (6-8)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"0","text":"- ¿Cómo se\\Ndiagnostica la\\NBF?","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"0","text":"- TCAR: Nódulos\\Ncentrolobulillares,\\Natrapamiento aéreo, vidrio\\Nesmerilado (9)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"0","text":"- Biopsia pulmonar quirúrgica: Folículos\\Nlinfoides con centros germinales\\Nalrededor de bronquiolos (10)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"0","text":"- ¿Cuál es el\\Ntratamiento de la\\NBF?","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"0","text":"- Corticoides sistémicos (respuesta variable,\\Nrecaídas frecuentes), rituximab (mejoría clínica y\\Nradiológica en series de casos), tratamiento de\\Nenfermedad subyacente (12-14)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"0","text":"Definición:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"0","text":"- La BF es una enfermedad pulmonar\\Nintersticial linfoide infrecuente,\\Ncaracterizada por hiperplasia linfoide\\Nreactiva alrededor de los bronquiolos (1)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"0","text":"- Descrita por primera vez por\\NBienenstock et al. en 1973 en\\Nasociación con artritis reumatoide (17)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"0","text":"- Infiltración linfocítica peribronquiolar\\N→ Formación de folículos linfoides con\\Ncentros germinales (1)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"0","text":"- Posible papel de citocinas (CXCL13,\\NCCL21) en el reclutamiento y\\Norganización de linfocitos (5)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"0","text":"- Objetivos\\Nterapéuticos:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"0","text":"- Suprimir la respuesta inflamatoria y la\\Nformación de folículos linfoides con\\Ncorticoides o rituximab (12,13)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"0","text":"- Tratar la enfermedad\\Nsubyacente (autoinmune,\\Ninmunodeficiencia) (14)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"0","text":"- Investigación futura:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"0","text":"- Esclarecer los mecanismos\\Nmoleculares de la formación de\\Nfolículos linfoides en la BF","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"0","text":"- Desarrollar terapias dirigidas a las\\Nvías de señalización involucradas\\N(ej. CXCL13, CCL21)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"0","text":"- Prevalencia e incidencia exactas\\Ndesconocidas, debido a la rareza\\Nde la enfermedad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"0","text":"- No hay datos\\Nespecíficos para Chile","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"0","text":"- Contribuye a la morbilidad respiratoria en\\Npacientes con enfermedades autoinmunes e\\Ninmunodeficiencias (15)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"0","text":"- Potencial progresión a\\Nfibrosis pulmonar y\\Ndiscapacidad respiratoria (16)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"0","text":"Factores de riesgo:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"0","text":"- Enfermedades autoinmunes: Artritis\\Nreumatoide (RR 8.0), síndrome de\\NSjögren (RR 6.0) (2,18)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"0","text":"- Inmunodeficiencias: VIH\\N(RR 5.0),\\Nhipogammaglobulinemia (RR\\N4.0) (3,19)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"0","text":"- Trasplante de médula ósea o\\Npulmón (RR 3.0) (4,20)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"0","text":"Causas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"0","text":"- Enfermedades\\Nautoinmunes (40-50%)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"0","text":"- Artritis reumatoide","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"0","text":"- Síndrome de Sjögren","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"0","text":"- Inmunodeficiencias\\N(30-40%)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"0","text":"- VIH","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"0","text":"- Hipogammaglobulinemia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"0","text":"- Postrasplante\\N(10-20%)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"0","text":"- Médula ósea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"0","text":"- Pulmón","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"0","text":"- Idiopática (5-10%)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"0","text":"Clínica:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"0","text":"- Antecedentes:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"0","text":"- Enfermedad autoinmune,\\Ninmunodeficiencia o trasplante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"0","text":"- Inicio insidioso,\\Ncurso crónico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"0","text":"- Cuadro clínico:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"0","text":"- Tos seca\\N(80%, OR 5.0)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"0","text":"- Disnea de esfuerzo\\N(70%, OR 4.5)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"0","text":"- Sibilancias\\N(50%, OR 3.0)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"0","text":"- Infecciones respiratorias\\Nrecurrentes (30%, OR 2.5)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"0","text":"- Factores de mal\\Npronóstico:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"0","text":"- Enfermedad\\Nautoinmune activa (RR\\N2.0)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"0","text":"- Inmunosupresión\\Nsevera (RR 2.5)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"0","text":"- Complicaciones:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"0","text":"- Fibrosis pulmonar\\N(10%, OR 4.0)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"0","text":"- Insuficiencia\\Nrespiratoria (5%, OR 6.\\N0)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"0","text":"Estudio:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"0","text":"- TCAR (S 90%,\\NE 70%) (9)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"0","text":"- Nódulos\\Ncentrolobulillares","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"0","text":"- Atrapamiento aéreo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"0","text":"- Vidrio esmerilado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"0","text":"- Biopsia pulmonar\\Nquirúrgica (S 95%, E 90%)\\N(10)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"0","text":"- Folículos linfoides con\\Ncentros germinales\\Nalrededor de bronquiolos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"0","text":"- Pruebas de\\Nfunción pulmonar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"0","text":"- Patrón restrictivo\\N(60%, OR 3.5)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"0","text":"- Disminución de\\NDLCO (80%, OR 5.0)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"0","text":"- Laboratorio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"0","text":"- Linfopenia\\N(50%, OR 2.0)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"0","text":"- Hipergammaglobulinemia\\N(40%, OR 1.8)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"0","text":"- Diagnóstico de trabajo:\\NEnfermedad pulmonar\\Nintersticial con sospecha de BF\\N(1)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"0","text":"- Criterios diagnósticos\\N(requiere todos):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"0","text":"1. Clínica e\\Nimágenes\\Ncompatibles","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"0","text":"2. Exclusión de\\Notras causas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"0","text":"3. Biopsia pulmonar con\\Nhallazgos típicos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"0","text":"- Gold standard: Biopsia pulmonar\\Nquirúrgica (S 95%, E 90%) (10)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"0","text":"Diagnósticos\\Ndiferenciales:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"0","text":"- Neumonía intersticial no\\Nespecífica (NINE)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"0","text":"- Neumonitis por\\Nhipersensibilidad (NH)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"0","text":"- Bronquiolitis respiratoria\\Ncon enfermedad pulmonar\\Nintersticial (BR-EPI)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"0","text":"- Sarcoidosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"0","text":"- Linfoma\\Npulmonar\\Nprimario","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"0","text":"- Objetivo: Suprimir la inflamación y\\Nprevenir la progresión a fibrosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"0","text":"- No farmacológico:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"0","text":"- Suspender\\Ntabaquismo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"0","text":"- Evitar factores\\Ndesencadenantes (alérgenos,\\Nfármacos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"0","text":"- Farmacológico:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"0","text":"1. Primera línea: Prednisona 0.5-1\\Nmg/kg/día VO por 4-8 semanas, luego\\Ndisminuir gradualmente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"0","text":"- Respuesta variable,\\Nrecaídas frecuentes (12)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"0","text":"- Efectos adversos:\\NHiperglicemia, hipertensión,\\Nosteoporosis, infecciones","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"0","text":"2. Segunda línea: Rituximab 1000\\Nmg IV cada 2 semanas x 2 dosis,\\Nluego cada 6-12 meses","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"0","text":"- Mejoría clínica y radiológica\\Nen series de casos (13)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"0","text":"- Efectos adversos: Reacciones\\Ninfusionales, infecciones,\\Nleucoencefalopatía multifocal\\Nprogresiva","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"0","text":"3. Tratamiento de\\Nenfermedad subyacente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"0","text":"- Control de actividad de\\Nenfermedad autoinmune","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"0","text":"- Optimización de terapia\\Nantirretroviral en VIH","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"0","text":"- Ajuste de\\Ninmunosupresión en\\Ntrasplante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"0","text":"- Consideraciones:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"0","text":"- Prednisona: Metabolismo\\Nhepático (CYP3A4), vida media 3-4\\Nhoras, precio $5.000/mes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"0","text":"- Rituximab: Anticuerpo monoclonal\\Nanti-CD20, vida media 30 días,\\Nprecio $2.000.000/dosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"0","text":"Seguimiento y\\Npronóstico:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"0","text":"- No hay escalas validadas\\Npara determinar frecuencia\\Nde seguimiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"0","tex